### CSS Images

Style images for responsive, attractive layouts.

---

### Responsive Images

```css
img {
  max-width: 100%;
  height: auto;
}
```

Prevents overflow on small screens. Never wider than parent.

---

### Object Fit

```css
img {
  width: 300px;
  height: 200px;
  object-fit: cover;    /* Crops to fill (like background-size: cover) */
  object-fit: contain;  /* Fits inside (like background-size: contain) */
  object-fit: fill;     /* Stretches to fill (default) */
  object-fit: none;     /* Original size */
  object-fit: scale-down; /* Smaller of contain or none */
}
```

---

### Object Position

```css
img {
  object-fit: cover;
  object-position: center top;  /* Focus on top-center */
  object-position: 20% 80%;     /* Custom position */
}
```

---

### Image Rounded Corners

```css
img {
  border-radius: 8px;
}

/* Circle */
.avatar {
  width: 80px;
  height: 80px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  object-fit: cover;
}
```

---

### Image Filters

```css
img {
  filter: grayscale(100%);
  transition: filter 0.3s;
}

img:hover {
  filter: grayscale(0);
}
```

---

### Image Aspect Ratio

```css
img {
  aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
  object-fit: cover;
}
```

---

### Background Images

```css
.hero {
  background-image: url('hero.jpg');
  background-size: cover;
  background-position: center;
  background-repeat: no-repeat;
}
```

---

### Image Gallery Grid

```css
.gallery {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
  gap: 15px;
}

.gallery img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 250px;
  object-fit: cover;
  border-radius: 8px;
  transition: transform 0.3s;
}

.gallery img:hover {
  transform: scale(1.05);
}
```

---

> **Best Practice:** Always set `max-width: 100%` and `height: auto` on images for responsiveness.
